WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.920
Let's build a Python dashboard to impress your crush with your football knowledge.

00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:08.160
With this dashboard, you can surface quick facts, football terms, game situations,

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:11.040
all as your cheat sheet to winning over your crush's heart.

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:13.120
To build this is actually so simple.

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:17.040
Step one is to create a nav panel for each of the types of information.

00:00:17.040 --> 00:00:21.120
For my dashboard, I wanted to surface some quick facts, football terms, and game situations,

00:00:21.120 --> 00:00:23.440
but you can swap these out with literally anything that you want.

00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:26.799
Step number two is create a card with a new fact button.

00:00:26.799 --> 00:00:30.959
This is the button that will select a random fact from the right category and display it on the card.

00:00:30.959 --> 00:00:35.919
And step three, use chatGBT or the internet or whatever to generate a list of fun facts

00:00:35.919 --> 00:00:38.959
that fit the topics you want to know about and upload it to your web app.

00:00:38.959 --> 00:00:41.680
Once you're done building, you can deploy your app to Connect Cloud

00:00:41.680 --> 00:00:45.040
or use ShinyLive to view it on your phone during the next football game.

00:00:45.040 --> 00:00:47.520
Now you're ready to impress your crush all season long.

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:49.520
Make sure to follow along for more data science content.

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:50.000
Bye!

